profile.description: Four-spacecraft constellation studying magnetic reconnection in Earth's magnetosphere
data_caveats: Magnetospheric orbit â€” not solar wind data
Very high cadence burst data available for reconnection events
HAPI dataset IDs use @0/@1 suffixes: @0 = field/moment data, @1 = position/support data. Always use the @0 suffix for science data (e.g., MMS1_FGM_SRVY_L2@0)
analysis_patterns: Reconnection signatures: look for B reversal + jet in V
Magnetopause crossings: rapid B direction changes
